# Styling Conventions

## CSS custom properties only

Never hardcode color values. Use Material 21 CSS variables:

```scss
// BAD
color: #1a73e8;
background: rgb(255, 255, 255);

// GOOD
color: var(--mat-sys-primary);
background: var(--mat-sys-surface);
```

## Enterprise theme overrides

Place enterprise styling in `src/enterprise/styles/`. Override upstream variables, never upstream stylesheets.

## Light and dark theme

Both themes must be supported. Use `--mat-sys-*` variables that automatically adapt. Test both themes visually when adding UI.

## Angular Material 21

Use Material components and their theming APIs. Avoid custom implementations of standard UI patterns (buttons, dialogs, menus, tabs).
